title: Transatlantic - SMPTe (2000)
description:
From Wikipedia: 

SMPT:e (AKA StoltMorsePortnoyTrewavas) is the first album of the progressive rock supergroup Transatlantic. The title is a play on words; SMPT:e is both a combination of the band members' initials and the name of a recording technique.

All songs by Neal Morse/Mike Portnoy/Pete Trewavas/Roine Stolt, except where noted.
